decks.notes: The deck focuses on utilizing cheap spells and efficient creatures to quickly apply pressure to the opponent and win the game before they can stabilize. By casting a variety of low-cost instant and sorcery spells, the deck can trigger Veyran's ability to copy those spells, doubling the impact and damage dealt. This aggressive strategy is complemented by the diverse selection of creatures with prowess and other abilities that can snowball out of control if not dealt with swiftly. The land base is optimized for consistent mana production to ensure a steady stream of spells can be cast each turn. Overall, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent with a flurry of spells and creatures to secure a swift victory.
